  "intro": [
    {
      "title": "The Rifts",
      "lines": [
        "The shelf is all that holds — black void on three sides, stars in the deep where the ground used to be.",
        "Shots die in the rifts. So does anyone shoved off the causeway. Your only real front is the long diagonal up from the southwest.",
